                            <comment id="13906764" author="fenghh" created="Thu, 20 Feb 2014 08:45:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch attached for the fix&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And two minor changes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;exit immediately without sleep if isActive()==false after each failed try&lt;/li&gt;
